Weather South Africa are expecting severe damaging winds in the Kouga areas along the Garden Route in Jeffreys Bay and Patensie surrounding areas today, as well as in Port Elizabeth in Nelson Mandela Bay all most parts of the the day until approximately 15:00 this afternoon.There are also precautionary warnings along the Wild Coast in Port Alfred, Peddie and East London surrounding areas for most parts of the day until approximately 18:00 this evening. Residents in these areas are encouraged to be prepared and be on the watch-out for potemntial damaging winds.